<li sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-accrue.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50"><p sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-accrue.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">To set up a recurring job, select <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-accrue.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">Recurrence</strong>, enter the recurrence information, and the select <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-accrue.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">OK</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-accrue.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52"><p sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-accrue.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">To set up a job alert, select <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-accrue.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">Alerts</strong>, select the alerts to receive, and then select <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-accrue.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">OK</strong>.</p>
