<li sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-accrue.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54"><p sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-accrue.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">Select <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-accrue.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">OK</strong>. The accrual process will run with the parameters you set.</p>
